text: Flavors of Entanglement is the seventh studio album by rock singer Alanis Morissette. This studio album was released June 10, 2008 in the United States, June 9, 2008 in Australia, and on May 30, 2008 in Europe. Some singles from this album were: "Underneath", "Not As We", and "In Praise of the Vulnerable Man". ==Singles== ===2008=== *"Underneath" *"In Praise of the Vulnerable Man" *"Not As We" ==Track listing== #"Citizen of the Planet" – 4:22 #"Underneath" – 4:07 #"Straitjacket" – 3:08 #"Versions of Violence" – 3:36 #"Not As We" – 4:45 #"In Praise of the Vulnerable Man" – 4:07 #"Moratorium" – 5:35 #"Torch" – 4:50 #"Giggling Again for No Reason" – 3:48 #"Tapes" – 4:26 #"Incomplete" – 3:30 Category:2008 albums Category:Alanis Morissette albums
